{{Vgname|tw=星海爭霸II：諾娃特務密令|cn=星际争霸II：诺娃隐秘行动|en=StarCraft II: Nova Covert Ops}}是[[可下载内容|可下载内容]]（DLC）單人任務包，可用於[[軍事科幻|軍事科幻]][[即时战略游戏|即时战略游戏]]《[[星海爭霸II|星海爭霸II]]》，以幽能特務諾汎碧「諾娃」泰拉為故事核心。它由九個任務組成，作為DLC分三期發布，每個任務三個任務<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/videos/gs-news-update-blizzard-say-warcraft-4-and-starcra/2300-6428061/|title=GS News Update: Blizzard Say Warcraft 4 And StarCraft 3 Development "Depends On the Players"|publisher=|access-date=2018-12-15|archive-date=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207192406/https://www.gamespot.com/videos/gs-news-update-blizzard-say-warcraft-4-and-starcra/2300-6428061/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第一個任務包於2016年3月29日發布，第二個任務包於2016年8月2日發布，最終任務包於2016年11月22日發布<ref>{{cite web|url=https://us.battle.net/shop/en/product/starcraft-ii-nova-covert-ops|title=Nova Covert Ops|publisher=|access-date=2018-12-15|archive-date=2017-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170621101203/https://us.battle.net/shop/en/product/starcraft-ii-nova-covert-ops|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/third-and-final-mission-for-pack-starcraft-2s-nova-covert-ops-due-november-22/|title=Third and final mission for pack StarCraft 2's Nova Covert Ops due November 22|publisher=PC Gamer|access-date=2018-12-15|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108114911/https://www.pcgamer.com/third-and-final-mission-for-pack-starcraft-2s-nova-covert-ops-due-november-22/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 開發 ==
《[[星海爭霸II：虛空之遺|星海爭霸II：虛空之遺]]》的作者詹姆斯·沃（James Waugh）擔諾娃特務密令的故事總監，瓦樂莉·沃特勒斯（Valerie Watrous）是「虛空之遺」的合著者，也是主要作者。諾娃特務密令展示了暴雪可以更快速發布內容的可能<ref name="SCFuture">{{cite web |url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/11/6/9670176/starcraft-2-future-history-dlc-blizzard |title=StarCraft: The past, present and future |accessdate=October 5, 2016 |author=Megan Farokhmanesh |date=November 6, 2015 |publisher=[[Polygon|Polygon]] |deadurl=no |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227130604/https://www.polygon.com/2015/11/6/9670176/starcraft-2-future-history-dlc-blizzard }}</ref>。

== 評價 ==
任務包1和任務包2得到褒贬不一的反應。IGN指出前兩個任務包的故事乏味且篇幅太短<ref name="IGN Review 1">{{cite web |url=http://au.ign.com/articles/2016/04/05/starcraft-2-nova-covert-ops-mission-pack-1-review |title=StarCraft 2: Nova Covert Ops Mission Pack 1 Review |accessdate=October 5, 2016 |author=TJ Hafer |date=April 5, 2016 |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |deadurl=no |archive-date=2019-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219101040/https://au.ign.com/articles/2016/04/05/starcraft-2-nova-covert-ops-mission-pack-1-review }}</ref><ref name="IGN Review 2">{{cite web |url=http://au.ign.com/articles/2016/08/04/starcraft-2-nova-covert-ops-mission-pack-2-review |title=StarCraft 2: Nova Covert Ops Mission Pack 2 Review |accessdate=August 4, 2016 |author=TJ Hafer |date=April 5, 2016 |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |deadurl=no |archive-date=2019-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219101040/https://au.ign.com/articles/2016/08/04/starcraft-2-nova-covert-ops-mission-pack-2-review }}</ref>。

